      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f : \\R \\to \\R$ une fonction de classe $\\mathcal{C}^n$.\nOn pose $g(x) = f(x^2)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : \\R \\to \\R\\)</span> une fonction de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^n\\)</span>. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(g(x) = f(x^2)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8845b369-f3a3-4e60-87b3-db60a0bf99f0",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer qu'il existe des entiers $a_{n,k}$ tels que :\n    $\\forall\\ x,\\ g^{(n)}(x) = \\sum_{k= [(n+1)/2]}^n a_{n,k}f^{(k)}(x^2)(2x)^{2k-n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer qu’il existe des entiers <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_{n,k}\\)</span> tels que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x,\\ g^{(n)}(x) = \\sum_{k= [(n+1)/2]}^n a_{n,k}f^{(k)}(x^2)(2x)^{2k-n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "920324d5-0ddb-4496-9e19-b15afb45c58e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a_{n+1,k} = a_{n,k-1} + 2(2k-n)a_{n,k}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_{n+1,k} = a_{n,k-1} + 2(2k-n)a_{n,k}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "aaa66c62-c317-497f-a578-caeb308d43df",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $a_{n,k}$ en fonction de $n$ et $k$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_{n,k}\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c86278d8-f1d1-49f9-a06e-82deb4190173",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a_{n,k} = \\frac {n!}{(n-k)!(2k-n)!}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_{n,k} = \\frac {n!}{(n-k)!(2k-n)!}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
